### Distribution packages

Here's a list of packages, ready to install for the respective
distributions:

* [Arch Linux (AUR)](http://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?ID=45324)
* [Gentoo (James Rowe's misc-overlay)](http://jnrowe.github.com/jnrowe-misc-docs/packages/dev-vcs.html)
* [Debian Sid](http://packages.debian.org/unstable/main/pepper)
* [Ubuntu Raring Ringtail](http://packages.ubuntu.com/raring/vcs/pepper)

For source packages, please remember to install optional build-time
dependencies for the repository backends first (e.g., `subversion`
and `mercurial` on Arch Linux).

Thanks to all maintainers!


